#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya12, sc20
msgctxt "mn78:12.1"
msgid "Katame ca, thapati, akusalā saṅkappā? "
msgstr "And what are unskillful thoughts? "

msgctxt "mn78:12.2"
msgid "Kāmasaṅkappo, byāpādasaṅkappo, vihiṃsāsaṅkappo—"
msgstr "Thoughts of sensuality, of malice, and of cruelty. "

msgctxt "mn78:12.3"
msgid "ime vuccanti, thapati, akusalā saṅkappā. "
msgstr "These are called unskillful thoughts. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc21
msgctxt "mn78:12.4"
msgid "Ime ca, thapati, akusalā saṅkappā kiṃsamuṭṭhānā? "
msgstr "And where do these unskillful thoughts stem from? "

msgctxt "mn78:12.5"
msgid "Samuṭṭhānampi nesaṃ vuttaṃ. "
msgstr "Where they stem from has been stated. "

msgctxt "mn78:12.6"
msgid "‘Saññāsamuṭṭhānā’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "You should say that they stem from perception. "

msgctxt "mn78:12.7"
msgid "Katamā saññā? "
msgstr "What perception? "

msgctxt "mn78:12.8"
msgid "Saññāpi hi bahū anekavidhā nānappakārakā. "
msgstr "Perception takes many and diverse forms. "

msgctxt "mn78:12.9"
msgid "Kāmasaññā, byāpādasaññā, vihiṃsāsaññā—"
msgstr "Perceptions of sensuality, malice, and cruelty—"

msgctxt "mn78:12.10"
msgid "itosamuṭṭhānā akusalā saṅkappā. "
msgstr "unskillful thoughts stem from this. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.28, sc22
msgctxt "mn78:12.11"
msgid "Ime ca, thapati, akusalā saṅkappā kuhiṃ aparisesā nirujjhanti? "
msgstr "And where do these unskillful thoughts cease without anything left over? "

msgctxt "mn78:12.12"
msgid "Nirodhopi nesaṃ vutto. "
msgstr "Their cessation has also been stated. "

msgctxt "mn78:12.13"
msgid "Idha, thapati, bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi … pe … paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati; "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant, quite secluded from sensual pleasures, secluded from unskillful qualities, enters and remains in the first absorption, which has the rapture and bliss born of seclusion, while placing the mind and keeping it connected. "

msgctxt "mn78:12.14"
msgid "etthete akusalā saṅkappā aparisesā nirujjhanti. "
msgstr "This is where these unskillful thoughts cease without anything left over. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc23
msgctxt "mn78:12.15"
msgid "Kathaṃ paṭipanno ca, thapati, akusalānaṃ saṅkappānaṃ nirodhāya paṭipanno hoti? "
msgstr "And how is someone practicing for the cessation of unskillful thoughts? "

