#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya13, sc24
msgctxt "mn78:13.1"
msgid "Katame ca, thapati, kusalā saṅkappā? "
msgstr "And what are skillful thoughts? "

msgctxt "mn78:13.2"
msgid "Nekkhammasaṅkappo, abyāpādasaṅkappo, avihiṃsāsaṅkappo—"
msgstr "Thoughts of renunciation, good will, and harmlessness. "

msgctxt "mn78:13.3"
msgid "ime vuccanti, thapati, kusalā saṅkappā. "
msgstr "These are called skillful thoughts. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc25
msgctxt "mn78:13.4"
msgid "Ime ca, thapati, kusalā saṅkappā kiṃsamuṭṭhānā? "
msgstr "And where do these skillful thoughts stem from? "

msgctxt "mn78:13.5"
msgid "Samuṭṭhānampi nesaṃ vuttaṃ. "
msgstr "Where they stem from has been stated. "

msgctxt "mn78:13.6"
msgid "‘Saññāsamuṭṭhānā’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "You should say that they stem from perception. "

msgctxt "mn78:13.7"
msgid "Katamā saññā? "
msgstr "What perception? "

msgctxt "mn78:13.8"
msgid "Saññāpi hi bahū anekavidhā nānappakārakā. "
msgstr "Perception takes many and diverse forms. "

msgctxt "mn78:13.9"
msgid "Nekkhammasaññā, abyāpādasaññā, avihiṃsāsaññā—"
msgstr "Perceptions of renunciation, good will, and harmlessness—"

msgctxt "mn78:13.10"
msgid "itosamuṭṭhānā kusalā saṅkappā. "
msgstr "skillful thoughts stem from this. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc26
msgctxt "mn78:13.11"
msgid "Ime ca, thapati, kusalā saṅkappā kuhiṃ aparisesā nirujjhanti? "
msgstr "And where do these skillful thoughts cease without anything left over? "

msgctxt "mn78:13.12"
msgid "Nirodhopi nesaṃ vutto. "
msgstr "Their cessation has also been stated. "

msgctxt "mn78:13.13"
msgid "Idha, thapati, bhikkhu vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā … pe … dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati; "
msgstr "It’s when, as the placing of the mind and keeping it connected are stilled, a mendicant enters and remains in the second absorption, which has the rapture and bliss born of immersion, with internal clarity and confidence, and unified mind, without placing the mind and keeping it connected. "

msgctxt "mn78:13.14"
msgid "etthete kusalā saṅkappā aparisesā nirujjhanti. "
msgstr "This is where these skillful thoughts cease without anything left over. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc27
msgctxt "mn78:13.15"
msgid "Kathaṃ paṭipanno ca, thapati, kusalānaṃ saṅkappānaṃ nirodhāya paṭipanno hoti? "
msgstr "And how is someone practicing for the cessation of skillful thoughts? "

